data.text: @CimFighter I can't even talk about that. First time I watched was 2014. 😂 before that when I would have even stayed up till kick off my parents would have killed me. 😂

@CimFighter Well I usually think his songs are pretty good but it's sad when you just take away the complete lead vocals. For sure they had much worse at the super bowl but they also had much better. And I was looking forward to the halftime show so it's really disappointing to me.
@CimFighter I didn't liked it at all. Haha. The end was good when he actually was singing but for most of the part he was just dancing and not singing at all. So disappointing. 😢💔
